                a(title='Groupon', href='http://groupon.com') Groupon
                |  (since 2016)

              p
                | In the past, I have interned at 
                a(title='CDK Global', href='http://cdk.com') CDK Global
                |  (2015), worked as webmaster for the 
                a(title='ASUW', href='http://asuw.org')
                  abbr(title='Associated Students of the University of Washington') ASUW
                |  (2014), and been a teaching assistant for various computer science courses at the 
                a(title='UW', href='http://uw.edu') University of Washington
                |  (2015&mdash;16).

          .row.narrow
            article.col.half
              header
